r s BC-BOX-CURRY-WRITETHRU-T     05-21 2096
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BOX-CURRY-WRITETHRU-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
EDS: FIXES SLUG 
HE FELL FROM TOP OF BOXING WORLD, NOW CURRY SEEKS FIGHTING CHANCE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By JOHN STURBIN 
c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
