u i BC-HAITI-ELECTION-ART-NY     05-21 1128
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HAITI-ELECTION-ART-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
HAITI HOLDS A LONG-DELAYED ELECTION 
</HEADLINE>
  (ART ADV: Map is being sent to NYT graphic clients. Nonsubscribers
can purchase one-time rights by calling 888-603-1036 or
888-346-9867.) 
