   &UR; BBQ _ &LR;  So you want to be an Internet entrepreneur? One day you see
that a terrific domain name _ BBQ.com _ is for sale, and you decide
to build an Internet store around it, selling $3,300 Lynx gas
grills, bacon-wrapped Omaha steaks, electric bug zappers.  &UR; BY &LR; 
 &UR; CAROLYN SAID &LR;
</P>
