<P>
   (NYT20) MIAMI -- May 21, 2000 -- BKN-KNICKS-HEAT-7 -- The New
York Knicks Patrick Ewing enjoys a moment of glory as the Knicks
defeated the Miami Heat 83-82, Sunday. The Knicks knocked the Heat
out of the playoffs for the third straight season to advance to the
Eastern Conference finals against Indiana. Game 1 is Tuesday night
in Indianapolis. (BartonSilverman/The New York Times)
